{"tid":309143,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［尋人］一個虛擬女友的神秘故事","createTime":"2017-07-04T18:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T13:58:20.000Z","uid":54342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b52ecf29cf7419bb1d839c0c213457e9f33b4745","tid":309143,"uid":54342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T18:00:36.000Z","msg":"我記得係高登時期 有位巴打開左個好多迷題既post<br />\n唔知仲有冇人記得<br />\n內容大致係咁：<br />\n<br />\n呢位巴位好鐘情於玩一隻online game 係呢隻game到認識左女主角 情投意合下大家成為左朋友 亦交換左電話 ig 同 fb 係呢個社交網絡入面了解到大家既生活模式<br />\n<br />\n佢知道呢個女仔係台灣人 雖然樣子身材都係女神級 但身邊既朋友並不多 係女仔ig出現既人物寥寥可數 亦冇男朋友 所以巴打開始苦心追求同表白 但換來只有失望  雖然屢戰屢敗 但佢冇放棄 一直維持住朋友關係 希望有一日能夠修成正果 <br />\n<br />\n有一日奇怪既事發生 巴打係google搵到張個女仔係ig po過既相 大家睇到呢到都會話 屌 有撚幾奇呀？<br />\n奇就奇在google既相係彩色 個女仔ig個張係黑白 一張相轉去黑白好簡單 但轉去彩色係唔可能 後來更加發呢個女仔原來已經扮左好幾年 ig入面既相全部都係偷人圖<br />\n<br />\n再後來既事已經記得唔清楚 依稀記得個結局係巴打發個女仔因爲火傷而令佢有少少精神病 但呢位巴打發現呢個秘密之後 個女仔就從此人間蒸發<br />\n<br />\n如果你睇到呢個post 可以講下你既近況嗎 有搵到佢嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f380a0826f8f37a63306a44f58282f6d82b90b","tid":309143,"uid":54342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T18:01:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98d44d1105514ae189428a4081289d28817ceea1","tid":309143,"uid":54342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T18:01:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cefe29191aa7c60cb3b0d5ede32773cc13d4e93e","tid":309143,"uid":54342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T18:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4dbb581dafaf98aeba2472c1baf96cc08c95804","tid":309143,"uid":71266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T18:02:43.000Z","msg":"痴線"},{"pid":"174021991d53d11f881be4d49b5434d7051876e1","tid":309143,"uid":54342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T18:04:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴線</blockquote><br />\n唔係痴線架 個po好傷感"},{"pid":"411d20912b3a08d28597cc79d21928ce7af68ea1","tid":309143,"uid":2431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T18:04:17.000Z","msg":"我都記得呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地好似有約過出嚟？"},{"pid":"9006bdf5ea1c00695d1f26721e67d0264dcfaec8","tid":309143,"uid":54342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T18:05:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都記得呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地好似有約過出嚟？</blockquote><br />\n就係出黎發現完個秘密就好似冇左下文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d70e345f1b84ae8c678409752eff91371814b3","tid":309143,"uid":54342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T18:07:39.000Z","msg":"唉 希望佢可以見到個po"},{"pid":"c1267fd81e6b128c0aaf596eac8d681ec3a227b5","tid":309143,"uid":54342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T18:07:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e983f4334a2133b70bb8ec6f7651f8ede242f153","tid":309143,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T18:11:31.000Z","msg":"樓主就係個女仔？"},{"pid":"935c523f41e7a729950a94fac920fdc3b369ee30","tid":309143,"uid":54342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T18:12:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主就係個女仔？</blockquote><br />\n樓主係巴打 個時佢仲有同個女仔whatsapp對話既圖"},{"pid":"20a8d6e51f14392529051e4e60e2380951b5ce43","tid":309143,"uid":54342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T23:55:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f7eb5f2ed2fe3ef7f968ea7cf0c4d